	<head>
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Customer Messaging & Appointment Reminders</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    /* ========= <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Customer Messaging Page ========= */

    .msg-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-green: #16a34a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 72px;
    }

    .msg-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .msg-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */

    .msg-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .msg-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .msg-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .msg-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .msg-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.2vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .msg-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .msg-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .msg-hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .msg-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .msg-hero-foot {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .msg-hero-foot span {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .msg-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .msg-hero-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .msg-hero-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .msg-hero-chip {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    }

    .msg-hero-status {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .msg-bubble-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .msg-bubble {
      max-width: 90%;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .msg-bubble.you {
      align-self: flex-end;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4f46e5, #6366f1);
      border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    }

    .msg-bubble.them {
      align-self: flex-start;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    .msg-bubble-label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .msg-bubble-text {
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .msg-template-row {
      margin-top: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .msg-template-row code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
        "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .msg-hero-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .msg-hero-footer span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .msg-hero-footer-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .msg-hero-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ---------- Intro text ---------- */

    .msg-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .msg-intro h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .msg-intro p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .msg-intro strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- 3 main feature rows ---------- */

    .msg-feature-section {
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    .msg-feature-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .msg-feature-block.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .msg-feature-block,
      .msg-feature-block.reverse {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .msg-feature-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .msg-feature-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .msg-feature-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .msg-feature-text + .msg-feature-text {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .msg-feature-highlight {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .msg-feature-list {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .msg-feature-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .msg-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .msg-feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .msg-feature-card p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .msg-feature-tag-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .msg-feature-tag {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .msg-feature-tag.alt {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #166534;
    }

    /* ---------- Testimonials ---------- */

    .msg-section-header {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .msg-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .msg-section-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .msg-section-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 560px;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 52px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .msg-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .msg-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .msg-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    }

    .msg-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-heading {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-person {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .msg-testimonial-person strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- Articles ---------- */

    .msg-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .msg-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .msg-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .msg-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .msg-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .msg-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .msg-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .msg-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .msg-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .msg-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- Newsletter ---------- */

    .msg-newsletter {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #111827, #020617);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .msg-newsletter {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .msg-newsletter h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .msg-newsletter p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .msg-newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .msg-newsletter-input {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      min-width: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      outline: none;
    }

    .msg-newsletter-input::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .msg-newsletter-btn {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .msg-newsletter-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="msg-page" id="customer-messaging">
  <div class="msg-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="msg-hero">
      <div>
        <h1 class="msg-title">
          Deliver great customer service with <span>clear, consistent communication.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="msg-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>’s customer messaging tools bring SMS, email and reminders into one place so you can
          send professional updates in a few clicks and keep every conversation tied to the right job.
        </p>
        <p class="msg-hero-note">
          Use smart tokens to automatically pull in appointment times, balances, addresses and more —
          without hunting through your diary or spreadsheets.
        </p>

        <div class="msg-cta-row">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">Which plan?</a>
        </div>
        <p class="msg-hero-foot">
          <span>Works with your existing <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> schedule and customer records.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: messaging mockup -->
      <div class="msg-hero-media">
        <div class="msg-hero-card">
          <div class="msg-hero-header">
            <div class="msg-hero-chip"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> · 2-way messaging</div>
            <div class="msg-hero-status">All replies in one inbox</div>
          </div>

          <div class="msg-bubble-list">
            <div class="msg-bubble them">
              <span class="msg-bubble-label">Customer · SMS</span>
              <span class="msg-bubble-text">Hi, can you confirm what time you’re coming tomorrow?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="msg-bubble you">
              <span class="msg-bubble-label">You · Template</span>
              <span class="msg-bubble-text">
                Hi Sarah — your next appointment is
                <strong>{{next_appointment_time}}</strong>. You can see all visits and invoices in
                your <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> portal.
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="msg-bubble them">
              <span class="msg-bubble-label">Customer · SMS</span>
              <span class="msg-bubble-text">Perfect, thank you!</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="msg-template-row">
            Current template: <code>Reminder – {{customer_name}} · {{next_appointment_date}}</code>
          </div>

          <div class="msg-hero-footer">
            <span>
              <span class="msg-hero-footer-dot"></span>
              Live sync across web & mobile
            </span>
            <span>SMS · Email · Portal</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="msg-hero-shadow"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="msg-intro">
      <h2>Keep every customer in the loop, without drowning in messages.</h2>
      <p>
        <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> lets you send one-off messages, bulk updates and fully automated sequences from the
        same place you plan your work. Every message is tracked against the customer and the job so
        your team always has context.
      </p>
      <p>
        Build templates once, then insert live data using tokens like
        <strong>{{next_appointment_time}}</strong>, <strong>{{job_address}}</strong> or
        <strong>{{outstanding_balance}}</strong>. <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> does the heavy lifting so every message
        feels personal without taking extra time.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- MAIN FEATURES -->
    <section class="msg-feature-section">

      <!-- Customer Replies -->
      <article class="msg-feature-block">
        <div>
          <p class="msg-feature-label">Customer Replies</p>
          <h2 class="msg-feature-title">Never lose track of a reply again.</h2>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            Ask customers to text or email your <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> number and address. Every incoming message drops
            into a central feed so nothing gets buried in someone’s personal phone.
          </p>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            When a customer replies, you’ll see it alongside their history, balance and upcoming work.
            Anyone on your team can pick up the conversation and reply from the web or mobile app.
          </p>
          <ul class="msg-feature-list">
            <li>Shared inbox for SMS and email replies</li>
            <li>Instant alerts when new messages arrive</li>
            <li>Whole conversation history attached to the customer</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <aside class="msg-feature-card">
          <div class="msg-feature-tag-row">
            <span class="msg-feature-tag">Shared Inbox</span>
            <span class="msg-feature-tag alt">Team Visibility</span>
          </div>
          <h3>All replies, one place</h3>
          <p>
            The same message thread is visible to office staff and field workers, so everyone knows what
            was promised and when.
          </p>
        </aside>
      </article>

      <!-- Job status notifications -->
      <article class="msg-feature-block reverse">
        <aside class="msg-feature-card">
          <div class="msg-feature-tag-row">
            <span class="msg-feature-tag">Job Status</span>
            <span class="msg-feature-tag alt">Automation</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Automated status updates</h3>
          <p>
            Trigger notifications when jobs are scheduled, started, paused or completed — without adding
            extra steps for your team.
          </p>
        </aside>

        <div>
          <p class="msg-feature-label">Job Status Notifications</p>
          <h2 class="msg-feature-title">Keep customers informed from first booking to final invoice.</h2>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            Configure <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> to send automatic messages at key points in your workflow: when a job is
            booked, when the team is on the way, when it’s finished and when the invoice is ready.
          </p>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            Use different templates for different services or locations, and choose whether to send via
            SMS, email or both.
          </p>
          <ul class="msg-feature-list">
            <li>On-the-way and job-completed messages</li>
            <li>Different templates per service type</li>
            <li>Optional links to customer portal and payment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Appointment reminders -->
      <article class="msg-feature-block">
        <div>
          <p class="msg-feature-label">Appointment Reminders</p>
          <h2 class="msg-feature-title">Cut down on no-shows and last-minute cancellations.</h2>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            Choose how far in advance to send reminders — hours, days or weeks — and let <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> handle
            them automatically.
          </p>
          <p class="msg-feature-text">
            Combine reminder templates with tokens so each customer receives the right date, time and
            address, even when your schedule changes.
          </p>
          <ul class="msg-feature-list">
            <li>Flexible timing rules per service or route</li>
            <li>SMS, email or both, depending on customer preference</li>
            <li>Optional follow-up messages when customers don’t respond</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <aside class="msg-feature-card">
          <div class="msg-feature-tag-row">
            <span class="msg-feature-tag">No-shows ↓</span>
            <span class="msg-feature-tag alt">Cashflow ↑</span>
          </div>
          <h3>Fewer gaps in the calendar</h3>
          <p>
            With clear reminders going out automatically, customers are more likely to be home, ready and
            expecting you.
          </p>
        </aside>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
    <section>
      <div class="msg-section-header">
        <p class="msg-section-kicker">What teams say about <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %></p>
        <h2 class="msg-section-title">Messaging that pays for itself in saved time.</h2>
        <p class="msg-section-sub">
          See how service businesses use <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> messaging and reminders to reduce admin, keep schedules
          full and improve customer satisfaction.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="msg-testimonial-grid">
        <article class="msg-testimonial-card">
